    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(SN) In nomine domini Dei eterni. Anno ab incarnatione eius millesimo
                        centesimo quadragesimo primo, die lune qui est de mense agusti, inditione
                        quarta. Dum domnus <persName
                            key="#Bishops #Domus #Laubia/topia #Witness #Judicial_breve"
                            ref="#people/3548">Magnifredus</persName>, venerabilis <placeName
                            key="#Bishops #Domus #Laubia/topia" ref="#places/9"
                            >Brixiensium</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>, in <rs key="#Domus">domo</rs> episcopali
                        audiret <rs>litem et controversiam</rs> que vertebatur inter domnum
                            <persName key="#Priors #Monasteries" ref="#people/3719"
                            >Iohannem</persName>, <rs key="#Priors">priorem</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">cenobii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Priors #Decima" ref="#juridical_persons/2066"
                            >Sancti Viti</orgName>, constructi in loco <placeName
                            key="#Monasteries #Baptismal_churches #Decima" ref="#places/2475"
                            >Methule</placeName>, nec non et inter <rs key="#Other_clerics"
                            >clericos</rs>
                        <rs key="#Baptismal_churches">plebis</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Baptismal_churches #Other_clerics #Decima"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2005">Sancte Marię</orgName> de predicto loco
                        Methule, nominative de <rs key="#Decima">decimis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Agricultural_workers">rusticorum</rs> predicti cenobii Sancti Viti
                        atque fructuum, quos predictus prior cum suis fratribus suis laboribus aut
                        sumptibus excolunt; aliisque etiam venerabilibus viris presentibus et causam
                        cum eo audientibus, videlicet <persName
                            key="#Archdeacons #Witness #Judicial_breve"><name ref="Paulus"
                                >Paulo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Archdeacons">archidiacono</rs> et <persName
                            key="#Archpriests #Witness #Judicial_breve"><name ref="Aldus"
                                >Aldo</name></persName> maioris Brixiensis ecclesie <rs
                            key="#Archpriests">archipresbitero</rs> atque domno <persName
                            key="#Abbots #Monasteries #Witness #Judicial_breve" ref="#people/3718"
                            >Iohanne</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abate</rs> monasterii <orgName key="#Monasteries #Abbots"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2459">Sanctorum martirum Faustini et
                            Iovitte</orgName> aliisque <rs key="#Canons">canonicis</rs> presentibus.
                        Ibi vero incontinenti predictus episcopus, consensu predictorum fratrum,
                        transegerit cum predicto Iohanne priore, qui etiam dicebat se hanc
                        transactionem facere consensu domni <persName key="#Abbots #Monasteries"
                            ref="#people/3568">Enrici</persName> abatis monasterii <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Abbots" ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti
                            Benedicti</orgName>, qui est constructum inter Padum et Larionem, eo
                        pacto et ea lege, ut suprascriptus Iohannes prior suique successores, qui
                        ibi pro tempore fuerint, de hinc in antea habeant decimas fructuum terre et
                        animalium quos propriis laboribus vel sumptibus excolunt, prout decreti
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1100">Romane sedis</orgName> decrevit
                        auctoritas, sine contradictione suprascripti episcopi suorumque successorum.
                        Predicta vero plebs Sancte Marię eiusque offitiales, qui nunc sunt ibi vel
                        pro tempore fuerint, de hinc in antea habeant decimas omnium fructuum
                        suprascriptorum rusticorum sine contradictione suprascripti prioris
                        suorumque successorum, quia sic inter eos convenit ut supra, salva tamen in
                        posterum hinc inde Romane sedis sancione. Actum est hoc in <rs
                            key="#Laubia/topia">laubia</rs> episcopali. Feliciter, ut supra. <rs
                            key="#Witness">Ibi fuere</rs>
                        <persName key="#Witness #Judicial_breve"><name ref="Raterius/de la Carza"
                                >Raterius</name></persName> de la Carza, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Judicial_breve"><name ref="Albertus/de Placentia"
                                >Albertus</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/43"
                            >Placentia</placeName> et <persName key="#Witness #Judicial_breve"><name
                                ref="Curbarardus">Curbarardus</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Judicial_breve"><name ref="Iohannes/de Eseno"
                                >Iohannes</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/4163"
                            >Eseno</placeName> canonicus et alii plures. + Ego Manfredus Brexiensis
                        episcopus subscripsi. Ego Paulus archidiaconus subscripsi. Ego Aldo
                        archipresbiter subscripsi. Ego Iohannes abbas subscripsi. (SN) Ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Judicial_breve"><name ref="Gherardus/legis peritus"
                                >Gerardus</name></persName>
                        <rs>legis peritus</rs>, rogatu suprascripti episcopi et prioris, hoc <rs
                            key="#Judicial_breve">bre[ve]</rs>
                        <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs> ut supra. Ego <persName
                            key="#Deacons #Witness #Judicial_breve"><name ref="Benedictus"
                                >Benedictus</name></persName>
                        <orgName key="#Deacons" ref="#juridical_persons/2411">Sancti Petri in
                            Oliveto</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs> subscripsi. </ab>
                </div>
